<h1 >冬小麦</h1>
<a href="javascript:;" class="edit-lemma cmn-btn-hover-blue cmn-btn-28 j-edit-link"><em class="cmn-icon wiki-lemma-icons wiki-lemma-icons_edit-lemma"></em>编辑</a>
<a class="lock-lemma" nslog-type="10003105" target="_blank" href="javascript:;" title="锁定"><em class="cmn-icon wiki-lemma-icons wiki-lemma-icons_lock-lemma"></em>锁定</a>
<a href="/planet/talk?lemmaId=508343" target="_blank" class="lemma-discussion cmn-btn-hover-blue cmn-btn-28 j-discussion-link" nslog-type="90000102"><em class="cmn-icon wiki-lemma-icons wiki-lemma-icons_discussion-solid"></em>讨论<span class="num"></span></a>
</dd>
</dl><div class="authorityListPrompt">
<div class="main-content-zj">
本词条由<a href="https://baike.baidu.com/science" target="_blank" class="nslog:7175">“科普中国”科学百科词条编写与应用工作项目</a>
审核
。</div>
</div>
<div class="promotion-declaration">
</div><div class="lemma-summary" label-module="lemmaSummary">
<div class="para" label-module="para">冬小麦，在我国一般以长城为界，以北大体为春小麦，以南则为冬小麦，我国以冬小麦为主。</div>
</div>
<div class="configModuleBanner">
</div><div class="basic-info cmn-clearfix">
<dl class="basicInfo-block basicInfo-left">
<dt class="basicInfo-item name">中文学名</dt>
<dd class="basicInfo-item value">
冬小麦
</dd>
<dt class="basicInfo-item name">界</dt>
<dd class="basicInfo-item value">
植物界
</dd>
<dt class="basicInfo-item name">门</dt>
<dd class="basicInfo-item value">
被子植物门 Angiospermae
</dd>
<dt class="basicInfo-item name">亚&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;门</dt>
<dd class="basicInfo-item value">
被子植物亚门
</dd>
<dt class="basicInfo-item name">纲</dt>
<dd class="basicInfo-item value">
单子叶植物纲 Monocotyledoneae
</dd>
</dl><dl class="basicInfo-block basicInfo-right">
<dt class="basicInfo-item name">目</dt>
<dd class="basicInfo-item value">
禾本目 Graminales
</dd>
<dt class="basicInfo-item name">科</dt>
<dd class="basicInfo-item value">
禾本科 Gramineae
</dd>
<dt class="basicInfo-item name">亚&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;科</dt>
<dd class="basicInfo-item value">
早熟禾亚科 Pooideae
</dd>
<dt class="basicInfo-item name">族</dt>
<dd class="basicInfo-item value">
小麦族 Triticeae
</dd>
<dt class="basicInfo-item name">属</dt>
<dd class="basicInfo-item value">
小麦属 Triticum
</dd>
</dl></div>
